   "[Formatting Styles] Dislikes": {"1": "Overly long paragraphs, e.g., a single block of text without breaks.", "2": "Complex titles, e.g., 'An In-Depth Analysis of the Saints' Recent Performances in the Context of Historical Data'", "3": "Technical jargon in footnotes, e.g., 'See Appendix A for detailed statistics'.", "4": "Lack of visual breaks, e.g., no images or line breaks.", "5": "Rigid structure, e.g., following a strict academic style that limits personal expression."}
